Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy \Nwhose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached \Nthe Fish-Man Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are looking to destroy \Nthe Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find \Nthemselves caught up in the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turmoil and involved in an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Hordy's merciless plot puts the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Island in unprecedented danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reset our history to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe out those phantoms who shut \Nthe island away from the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the Fish-Man Island back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-hoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you let me handle \Nit my way, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our minds were made up when \Nwe arrived at the plaza that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with Jimbei, we wouldn't \Nlet anyone harm the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it all up to us, Brother-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! I promise \NI won't let you be hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy's All-out Attack! Red Hawk Blasts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy in stripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be dead before you notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camouflage Carpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a voice around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zeo-san got...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that, Skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My weapon-destroying technique \Ncalled Body Sword Crush made...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the tip of your sword crumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stabbed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still has too much pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think that way and get defatted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Stumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just fumbled your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Oh?! I lost him again! Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Flail...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...66 Neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the last 2 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the true power of \Nthe Revive-Revive Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When people die,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their souls must go to the next world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to keep its existence in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,radiates a strong energy almost \Nlike other corporeal beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It enables me to rock a crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of people better than anybody \Nelse when I play music.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw them into my world and \Neven create illusions for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when my soul leaves my \Nbody, people can see me clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took down one of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What keeps me alive in this world \Nis neither bodily organs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...nor muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I've got a lot of spunk! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretending he wasn't surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in other words, as long \Nas my bones don't get damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your attack can't pierce me to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this sword cane which the Longarm \NTribe sharpened for me -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's called Soul Solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its soulful slash will make you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the cold air from the land of the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the "Freezing Sword"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Freezing Sword - how cool is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh no! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep it up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's gained skills \Nto go on to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure you all get \Ndrowned in the deep sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're a burden to the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hit me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush around, mole shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cookie-cutter shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...finished setting a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy-sama is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't let anyone harm the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were granted power from heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up! You can't stop the Noah now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you will lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm gonna finish the \Nwhole thing with this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't finish anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear - Armament!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let anyone die again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bite your arm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Red Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy-san defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hordy, the captain of \Nthe New Fish-Man Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finally!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi, take me to the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No way! Captain Hordy lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to the Noah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! For the island and all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeo-san, please! You know this island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy was chosen by heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some loser human could never beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if the Noah destroys the island, \Nwe're getting nothing anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death is another way to get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate humans even in death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tragedies will become our flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our grudge will never go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody will take it over \Nand get our revenge for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy and all \Nyou officers are insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans made us insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct all of your anger toward humans-bogon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are responsible for every single \Ndisaster that Fish-Men meet-zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are humans that terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, when you look at history,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,humans did horrible things to Fish-Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Sharley!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See it with your own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the plaza and up in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,humans are fighting against the \Npirates from the Fish-Man District!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a human, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some strange ones but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have to see it with your own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you have no \Nright to say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to look at things \Nwith an impartial eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who won't fight \Nto the death will get
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,killed by me in order to leave \Nyour hatred toward humans behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that to your own people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was close! Thank you, Skeleton Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never died before so don't \Ntalk like you know all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get killed and leave hatred \Nbehind? How ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is left behind when you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can leave behind is your bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very persuasive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like people who \Ndevalue the lives of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even stand their smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't have a nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you guys who are devaluing lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so impressive that none \Nof you is trying to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you humans will die once \Nthe Noah hits the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I can't tell if \Nyou're a human or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain - Luffy will become \Nthe King of the Pirates someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he wouldn't let anyone \Nharm the island and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can leave it all up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in him so there \Nis nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll do my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you disappear \Nin front of my eyes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't have eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this? Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's enough. Oh, I'm so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we finish this up, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! I've lost my swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna end this fight by \Nusing a daring technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the third step, you will get \Nshot by me and that'll be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop dreaming your stupid dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weakling! Are you crying sour grapes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, I'm losing my edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to bluff better in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I can actually do these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it here before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That little guy got bigger suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to go out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hordy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat crew finally \Ndemonstrates its true power...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and attempts to overpower \Nthe New Fish-Man Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Hordy, having derived \Nimmeasurable power from the Energy Steroids...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the severely wounded Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.99,0:23:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...grapple in a final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coming to an End! The Final \NDecisive Battle against Hordy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
